[Episode 6]

10
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:09,256
Do you mind

11
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:11,320
if I act as the witness?

12
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:15,360
Of course not.

13
00:01:15,720 --> 00:01:16,880
That'd be perfect.

14
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,040
Go on.

15
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:04,040
