♪ Ready to fire ♪

17
00:02:06,490 --> 00:02:07,820
♪ Born to survive ♪

18
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,296
What?

19
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:10,320
Getting cold feet?

20
00:02:11,040 --> 00:02:12,880
You can still surrender now.

21
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:15,970
♪ I'm the only queen ♪

22
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,097
Your turn.

23
00:02:17,121 --> 00:02:18,856
Maybe you'll be as lucky as me.

24
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,200
And the gun won't fire either.

25
