can never be erased ♪

280
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:36,520
♪ How to find the self I can't reclaim ♪

281
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:45,910
♪ Fly away, hear she says ♪

282
00:15:45,990 --> 00:15:49,936
♪ She'll fly out from
thorns of woven lies ♪

283
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:53,546
♪ Pierce the fog,
shatter this dream tonight ♪

284
00:15:53,570 --> 00:15:56,500
♪ Burn like fire ♪

285
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:59,940
♪ Just burn like fire ♪

286
00:16:00,150 --> 00:16:04,040
♪ The maze in the abyss starts to clear ♪

287
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:06,766
♪ Yet night keep on whispering ♪

288
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:09,930
♪ Surrender to fate,
no clear direction ahead ♪

289
00:16:10,210 --> 00:16:13,720
♪ She will rise as the dawn
that breaks the darkness ♪

290
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:20,250
♪ Never slowing down,
for tomorrow cannot be stopped ♪

291
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:24,216
♪ Surrender to love and find the way ♪

292
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:27,770
♪ Even if fate tries to forget her ♪

293
00:16:27,990 --> 00:16:34,520
♪ Never despair,
for the heart burns with endless light ♪

294
00:16:34,930 --> 00:16:36,780
♪ Waiting for dawn ♪

